These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: australian, colombian, brazilian, nigerian
1. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:nigerian is between Nationality:australian and Nationality:colombian##2
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Nationality:australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | australian | nigerian | colombian | brazilian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: apple, onion, plum, mango
1. Food:apple is on the left of Food:mango##1
2. Food:onion is in an odd position##4
3. Food:onion is on the left or right of Food:apple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | onion | apple | mango | plum |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: thriller, animation, horror, western
1. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:thriller##3
2. Movie-Genre:thriller is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:horror is between Movie-Genre:western and Movie-Genre:animation##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western | horror | animation |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
